com.almworks.sqlite4java
Interface SQLiteConstants

public interface SQLiteConstants

This interface lists SQLite constants that may be used with sqlite4java. Normally you don't need to use them.

Some error messages are produced by SQLite wrapper, these have names WRAPPER_*. For documentation on SQLite constants, see SQLite docs.

Author:
Igor Sereda
See Also:
list of constants in SQLite docs
